body.name: Cuties Baby Wipes | Unscented & Hypoallergenic | 12 Soft-Packs | 864 Total Wipes
features: GENTLE HYPOALLERGENIC CLEANSING: Made with natural Aloe & Vitamin E, our hypoallergenic wipes have what your baby needs & nothing they don't. They're free of chlorine, alcohol, oils, lotions & dyes.
CONVENIENT & DURABLE: Tri-Form Fabric construction includes 2 quilted outer layers with a strong inner layer to prevent tearing. Open & dispense one-handed with a push button lid & pop-up wipes.
COMPLETE CARE FOR BABY'S SENSITIVE SKIN: Thoughtfully designed. Responsibly made. Incredibly soft. Our diapers & wipes are soft, absorbent & safe because they're going on your baby's sensitive skin.
OUR SKINSMART PROMISE TO YOU: With our diapers & baby wipes, every decision we make is designed to help protect the health of your child's sensitive skin, from preemie to newborn to toddler & beyond!

CUTIES COMPLETE CARE: We specialize in baby care, offering comfort & protection for the sensitive skin of your newborn, infant or toddler. Try our thoughtfully designed diapers, wet wipes & training pants!

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Press-Open Lid Our super-handy press-open lid works with one hand. You know, when two are a luxury. Hypoallergenic Made with natural aloe and vitamin E, Cuties hypoallergenic wipes are free of alcohol, parabens, fragrances, and dyes. Strong and Soft Cuties wipes combine three layers of strength and softness for a super soft, super strong, super enjoyable diaper change. Take Them Anywhere Available by the case, there are twelve single packs of 72 wipes you can take anywhere: your bag, bathroom, nursery, car, or anywhere else.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 3, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very SIMILAR to KIRKLAND BRAND
reviews.reviewText: This is my first time using Cuties baby wipes and I’m glad I read the reviews before purchasing and I am not regretting it. I really think it’s similar to Kirkland brand baby wipes because that was all I was using. And just to mention, Cuties baby wipes DOES NOT have a foul smell like Kirkland brand does. Cuties wipes has a light scent (not strong) and does not stink! It feels comfy, durable, and soft! I was using Kirkland brand baby wipes all the way because I loved the way it felt and how durable it was but the smell was not so great. I do not enjoy using pampers, Huggies, etc… just because I felt like it sucked period! Even tho Kirkland brand may have more wipes than Cuties in a box, I will And from now on, choose Cuties baby wipes over anything. Plus Cuties wipes has a lid cover that’s easy to open. I’m so glad I gave Cuties baby wipes a try because I met my needs for my baby’s sake.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 26, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Better than pampers
reviews.reviewText: My son has really sensitive skin. He can only use certain brands of diapers and wipes. I was buying the pampers pure aqua diapers. They’re definitely on the pricey side, but they’re the only kind he could use without getting a rash. I read the reviews on these, and decided to chance it. I have to say they are the closest wipes I have found that are equal in quality, softness, and durability to the pampers wipes. They are truly fragrance free. We have not had any issues with a rash at all. I also love the fact that they come with the lock closure on them. It keeps them fresh and moist and keeps him (2 yrs old) out of them. I would definitely recommend.
